reviews.review_text: This Show Should be Available to Stream! First off I must say this is a dynamite show! The Uncle John's Band > Terrapin smokes & the Bird Song goes to new places with Brent's backing vocals. What bothers me is.... This show is out of PRINT and therefore no longer available to the general public unless you want to shell out bucks to Ebay or an Amazon Z seller. The second thing, is this show was NOT released in its entirety. The following songs were cut from the DVD & VHS release: Promised Land, Cold Rain And Snow, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Drums and the first three songs of the encore: Man Smart-Woman Smarter, Iko Iko & Banana Boat Song So how can you really say that this was released? And lastly, this was originally a FREE FM radio show and therefore should remain free... I hope those that agree with me will email this site and have them put it back up... Peace!
